```plantuml
@startuml castle-finance_vault-transaction-indexer
participant EventBridge as "EventBridge\n(Scheduler)"
participant IndexLambda as "index-transaction-ids\nLambda"
participant SolscanAPI as "Solscan API"
participant SNSTopic as "SNS Topic"
participant DownloadLambda as "download-raw-transaction\nLambda"
participant SQSQueue as "SQS Queue"
participant DynamoDBRaw as "DynamoDB\n(Raw Transactions)"
participant DynamoDBNorm as "DynamoDB\n(Normalized Transactions)"
participant NormalizeLambda as "normalize-raw-transaction\nLambda"

EventBridge -> IndexLambda: Scheduled trigger
activate IndexLambda
IndexLambda -> SolscanAPI: Fetch transaction IDs
SolscanAPI --> IndexLambda: Return transaction IDs
IndexLambda -> SNSTopic: Publish transaction IDs
deactivate IndexLambda

SNSTopic -> DownloadLambda: Notify new transactions
activate DownloadLambda
DownloadLambda -> SQSQueue: Poll for messages
SQSQueue --> DownloadLambda: Return transaction IDs
DownloadLambda -> SolscanAPI: Fetch raw transaction data
SolscanAPI --> DownloadLambda: Return raw transaction
DownloadLambda -> DynamoDBRaw: Store raw transaction
deactivate DownloadLambda

DynamoDBRaw -> NormalizeLambda: Stream new records
activate NormalizeLambda
NormalizeLambda -> DynamoDBRaw: Read raw transaction
DynamoDBRaw --> NormalizeLambda: Return raw data
NormalizeLambda -> NormalizeLambda: Normalize transaction data
NormalizeLambda -> DynamoDBNorm: Store normalized transaction
deactivate NormalizeLambda
@enduml
```